{"tid":1481338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[信不信由你] 就一次咁多！","createTime":"2019-08-17T16:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T16:17:59.000Z","uid":289747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee023b6bba2829766b7b780cd3baabba3206299","tid":1481338,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5b5ibe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5b5ibe.png&h=2f0b05dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4UwFcTNwKAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4UwFcTNwKAM&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1EwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=b5f46838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4UwFcTNwKAM</a><br />\n<br />\n原因有6點 :<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港人就算點敵對都好，亦唔會自己殘殺自己香港人。抗爭者意見不合，極少會傷害對方 ; 狗警分幫分派，亦甚少會害自己人。<br />\n但共產黨唔同，為咗政權，可以乜都做得出！共產黨對香港人一D感情都無，只係政治同經濟上嘅棋子，爛頭卒，可以隨時犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n2. 八九民運時，亦有國安/武警/公安等等，假扮抗爭者，向軍車投擲燃燒彈，燒死了幾名解放軍，共產黨就藉此出師有名，血腥鎮壓學生(這只是其中之一個原因)。<br />\n<br />\n3. 我哋就算幾撚憎D狗，甚至想殺狗，我相信好多人都係把口講一下，發洩一下情緒，一定唔會真係殺狗！最多都係要佢哋變<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;殘廢狗&rdquo;</span></span>或者<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;太監狗&rdquo;</span></span>。至少我係咁諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 而家民心所向，如果真有其事，共匪犧牲大量/幾隻狗，可以逆轉民意的話，共匪一定會咁做，何樂而不為？俾美英西方國家知道，佢出兵鎮壓係有道理嘅，出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n5. 有人會說我分化，又玩陰謀論，又乜又柒，ok唔緊要。818如果真係有假扮勇武嘅人，借真係自己勇武嘅人挑起情緒，這會成為一個很好嘅跳板，班假勇武支那畜心諗 : <span style=\"font-size: large;\">機會嚟啦飛雲！</span><br />\n香港班狗(包括我哋)對共匪嚟講，全無感情，可以隨時犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n6. 我知我P牌仔講嘢無人會信，或者你哋睇完得啖笑，不過我敢講，我係一個有勇有謀嘅勇武派！出得去，我每次都企到最前線。君子不立危牆之下，進有時，退有時。嚟場係一場持久戰！各位手足，就818一日咁多，一日咁多，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">踏上這無盡旅途...<br />\n過去飄散消散失散花火...<br />\n重燃起，重燃點起鼓舞，<br />\n或許到最後沒有完美句號，<br />\n仍然倔強冒險一一去征討！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要生一齊生，要死一齊死！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6197d1936c3e2e76fb6f7ea2db9f18b5d36f610","tid":1481338,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"次次有活動 你地就成撚日放流料 有邊次係講中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638d92abb71949bec17a820edd11c4abd74486cc","tid":1481338,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6197d1936c3e2e76fb6f7ea2db9f18b5d36f610","tid":1481338,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"次次有活動 你地就成撚日放流料 有邊次係講中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"不怕一萬，就怕萬一。<br />\n嚟場係一場漫長嘅持久戰，我預咗戰鬥到最後！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}